At least let her do something, even if it is embarrassing.

789
00:50:23,020 --> 00:50:25,020
Mr. Yun Pil Ju, you don't have to make a fool of yourself.

790
00:50:25,090 --> 00:50:27,560
Just having a reaction will do.

791
00:50:28,420 --> 00:50:31,360
You know what a Titanic parody is, don't you?

792
00:50:31,490 --> 00:50:32,890
I don't know.

793
00:50:32,960 --> 00:50:34,030
The takeaway has arrived!

794
00:50:34,100 --> 00:50:36,900
- Over here! Over here!
- It came!

795
00:50:36,900 --> 00:50:38,830
- How much is it?
- It's 20 000 won.
(Approximately $18.50.)

796
00:50:40,970 --> 00:50:42,770
- Everyone, dig in!
- Good.

797
00:50:44,970 --> 00:50:47,980
Let's eat together, shall we?
The kimbap is delicious.

798
00:50:48,040 --> 00:50:51,050
No, thanks. I don't want to eat.

799
00:50:56,990 --> 00:50:58,590
Does Mr. Yun Pil Ju hate kimbap?

800
00:50:58,650 --> 00:51:00,920
No, he's not picky.

801
00:51:00,990 --> 00:51:02,660
Why won't he eat?

802
00:51:02,720 --> 00:51:06,330
Just don't eat then!

803
00:51:27,220 --> 00:51:29,950
I'll be in the meeting room for now. Go eat dinner, then come back.

804
00:51:30,350 --> 00:51:32,620
Okay. But, unni!

805
00:51:32,620 --> 00:51:34,760
You've been eating chicken breast all day.

806
00:51:34,820 --> 00:51:36,690
Should I bring you a sandwich?

807
00:51:36,690 --> 00:51:40,500
Don't you know that I'm about to record a show? I'm afraid that even just by drinking water I'll get bloated.

808
00:51:40,560 --> 00:51:42,160
Think, why don't you!

809
00:51:43,830 --> 00:51:45,230
I'll be back.

810
00:52:05,320 --> 00:52:06,250
Oh?

811
00:52:09,190 --> 00:52:11,190
Now you've recognized me.

812
00:52:13,260 --> 00:52:14,460
What's that?

813
00:52:16,000 --> 00:52:16,730
Ramen.

814
00:52:16,800 --> 00:52:18,600
Ah... Ramen...

815
00:52:20,540 --> 00:52:21,940
And kimchi.
(Kimchi - National dish of Korea)

816
00:52:22,000 --> 00:52:24,470
Right, fried kimchi.

817
00:52:26,270 --> 00:52:27,480
Do you want to eat?

818
00:52:28,080 --> 00:52:33,480
I have a shoot tomorrow. Eating ramen will make me bloat.

819
00:52:49,770 --> 00:52:52,430
I'll just have one bite.

820
00:52:52,500 --> 00:52:53,700
Please go ahead.

821
00:53:15,920 --> 00:53:17,930
Aren't you going to eat this?

822
00:53:20,000 --> 00:53:28,140
Then, I'll just eat another bite with the fried kimchi.

823
00:54:26,060 --> 00:54:28,860
I've... I've eaten it all.

824
00:54:29,870 --> 00:54:31,800
Why did you let me? How could you just watch me eat it all?

825
00:54:31,870 --> 00:54:34,470
You just kept eating, so I didn't want to stop you.

826
00:54:35,000 --> 00:54:37,670
I'm going crazy! What am I going to do?

827
00:54:38,470 --> 00:54:40,410
It's just a bowl of ramen. How big a problem can it be?

828
00:54:40,480 --> 00:54:44,150
Do you know what this will do? What just one bowl of ramen will do to me when I go on that program?

829
00:54:44,210 --> 00:54:47,680
On the exact same day, pictures will be all over the Internet,

830
00:54:47,750 --> 00:54:49,480
with people arguing over whether Kang Se Ri is just fat,

831
00:54:49,550 --> 00:54:52,620
or if she just had an injection. Haven't you heard any of them?

832
00:54:52,690 --> 00:54:56,560
Ah really. I'm crazy, crazy, crazy.

833
00:55:04,570 --> 00:55:05,100
What should I do?

834
00:55:05,170 --> 00:55:08,900
Director Kim, I'm writing a prescription that I want you to send over.

835
00:55:08,970 --> 00:55:10,840
Boil the medicine immediately, and then send it to...

836
00:55:11,970 --> 00:55:13,110
Where should it be delivered to?

837
00:55:13,180 --> 00:55:14,510
To my house.

838
00:55:14,580 --> 00:55:17,910
Nonhyeon-dong, 234-5.

839
00:55:17,980 --> 00:55:20,180
Send the prescription to the address I'll give you.

840
00:55:20,250 --> 00:55:22,520
Please send it tomorrow, early in the morning.

841
00:55:22,580 --> 00:55:23,590
Yes.

842
00:55:24,850 --> 00:55:28,990
After eating, this medicine will help with the bloating.

843
00:55:31,060 --> 00:55:35,060
Just like that, you know my home address.

844
00:55:35,130 --> 00:55:36,800
I can't be telling just anyone.

845
00:55:36,870 --> 00:55:39,530
If you don't want other people to know, I can send it to another place instead.

846
00:55:39,600 --> 00:55:40,940
It's okay.

847
00:55:41,000 --> 00:55:44,940
But, my home address... Don't spread it around, all right?

848
00:55:45,010 --> 00:55:45,940
Fine.

849
00:55:47,810 --> 00:55:50,150
Then I will leave first.

850
00:55:50,550 --> 00:55:51,550
That...

851
00:55:53,220 --> 00:55:56,020
Since I've eaten your ramen, next time,

852
00:55:56,080 --> 00:55:57,820
I'll treat you to a meal.

853
00:56:03,090 --> 00:56:04,630
In that case...

854
00:56:04,690 --> 00:56:07,760
Instead of treating me, can I ask you for a favor?

855
00:56:07,830 --> 00:56:08,560
What is it?

856
00:56:08,630 --> 00:56:12,830
You know that Titanic parody segment in the fantasy date?

857
00:56:12,900 --> 00:56:14,640
Can I not do it?

858
00:56:18,040 --> 00:56:19,110
All right.

859
00:56:19,640 --> 00:56:20,780
Thank you so much!

860
00:56:21,840 --> 00:56:23,040
In that case, I'm off.

861
00:56:33,390 --> 00:56:35,390
It really was delicious.

862
00:56:36,990 --> 00:56:39,660
But I ate it too fast.

863
00:56:40,000 --> 00:56:42,600
How do I get up, I'm so embarrassed?

864
00:56:42,660 --> 00:56:45,200
I should've at least eaten a little slower so I could talk more.

865
00:56:45,270 --> 00:56:47,070
We never talk...

866
00:56:50,470 --> 00:56:51,810
Mr. Yun Pil Ju!

867
00:56:59,150 --> 00:57:02,350
Instead of buying you a meal, should I treat you to a movie?

868
00:57:47,460 --> 00:57:49,330
Today is the last day they're showing Fighter,

869
00:57:49,400 --> 00:57:51,800
but I still haven't seen it.

870
00:57:51,870 --> 00:57:54,070
Mr. Yun Pil Ju.

871
00:57:54,140 --> 00:57:56,610
Which of my boyfriend's movies have you seen?

872
00:57:56,670 --> 00:57:59,670
I haven't seen any of his movies.

873
00:58:00,080 --> 00:58:02,740
Two of his movies were major blockbusters.

874
00:58:03,150 --> 00:58:05,010
I don't really have a lot of interest in movies.

875
00:58:05,080 --> 00:58:09,750
Do you not like movies only because I'm pestering you?

876
00:58:09,820 --> 00:58:12,020
You aren't watching because you were forced to, right?

877
00:58:12,090 --> 00:58:16,160
Knowing Pil Ju, he wouldn't tag along to a place he has no interest in.

878
00:58:16,630 --> 00:58:21,300
Recently, it seems like he's is a fan of Dok Go Jin. He keeps asking me about stuff related to him.

879
00:58:21,360 --> 00:58:24,500
Mr. Yun Pil Ju, do you really do that?

880
00:58:26,030 --> 00:58:29,440
Yes, I really want to know what kind of person he is.

881
00:58:32,840 --> 00:58:35,910
You said it's the VIP screening lounge right? I'll go in first.

882
00:58:36,910 --> 00:58:39,380
Let me buy the food and beverages.

883
00:58:39,450 --> 00:58:42,120
Absolutely not.

884
00:58:42,180 --> 00:58:43,590
I hate people munching and slurping next to me while watching a movie.

885
00:58:43,650 --> 00:58:45,390
I can at least buy a Coke, right?

886
00:58:45,450 --> 00:58:47,860
If I'm sitting down for two hours, I'll definitely be thirsty.

887
00:58:47,920 --> 00:58:52,660
You can't. In this world, there's nothing more I hate than the sound of a straw being sucked.

888
00:58:52,730 --> 00:58:57,000
Can't I at least buy some squid? I won't make any noise.

889
00:58:57,130 --> 00:58:58,930
Nothing will be okay.

890
00:59:00,740 --> 00:59:03,670
Why do you always want to eat?

891
00:59:04,940 --> 00:59:06,810
He simply will not compromise.

892
00:59:06,880 --> 00:59:09,210
Representative Moon, I'm at the theater now.

893
00:59:10,680 --> 00:59:13,350
Well, don't let Dok Go Jin discover you.

894
00:59:13,420 --> 00:59:14,880
Just stay at a distance and see who she is.

895
00:59:14,950 --> 00:59:17,150
I'll just wait in front of the VIP hall and confirm who it is.

896
00:59:17,220 --> 00:59:20,690
Oh, and should I take pictures?

897
00:59:43,850 --> 00:59:46,450
Everybody's gone to buy food and drinks.

898
00:59:46,520 --> 00:59:47,650
Ah, yes.

899
00:59:49,320 --> 00:59:53,590
Mr. Yun Pil Ju, I have one thing to ask you.

900
00:59:53,660 --> 00:59:56,190
Last time during my fanmeeting,

901
00:59:56,260 --> 01:00:00,130
didn't you ask me if I was with my boyfriend?

902
01:00:00,200 --> 01:00:04,200
Why were you curious about that?

903
01:00:07,000 --> 01:00:10,070
For a person who doesn't care about celebrities,

904
01:00:10,140 --> 01:00:13,480
you seem quite interested in Dok Go Jin.

905
01:00:16,750 --> 01:00:22,020
Are you curious about what kind of person my boyfriend is?

906
01:00:27,020 --> 01:00:29,620
You guys should meet if there's an opportunity.

907
01:00:30,030 --> 01:00:31,890
With Dok Go Jin?

908
01:00:39,430 --> 01:00:42,240
Isn't that Ae Jeong noona?
(Noona - Older sister)

909
01:00:42,300 --> 01:00:44,770
Why would she go in there?

910
01:00:58,850 --> 01:01:00,590
So, it's Ae Jeong noona?!

911
01:01:08,060 --> 01:01:11,730
I can come this far.

912
01:01:13,270 --> 01:01:15,070
This is good.

913
01:01:22,010 --> 01:01:23,010
Aigoo!
(Aigoo - Oh Dear, Oh My God)

914
01:01:36,890 --> 01:01:42,160
Look at that hat hair! Wearing a hat with this type of hair doesn't match at all.

915
01:01:44,500 --> 01:01:49,170
What should I do? Should I tell Representative Moon about this?

916
01:01:51,110 --> 01:01:52,310
Jae Seok?

917
01:01:56,040 --> 01:01:57,580
Are you here to catch a movie?

918
01:01:59,180 --> 01:02:02,250
Today's the last showing of Fighter,

919
01:02:02,320 --> 01:02:03,920
so you came to see that?

920
01:02:03,990 --> 01:02:05,650
Good then, I'm here with my team.

921
01:02:05,720 --> 01:02:07,390
Let's watch it together.

922
01:02:07,990 --> 01:02:11,190
Yun Pil Ju. Today you will get to meet him, all right?

923
01:02:11,260 --> 01:02:12,130
Are you okay with that?

924
01:02:12,190 --> 01:02:13,460
Yes.

925
01:02:14,730 --> 01:02:17,730
Where's Dok Go oppa? Did he go in already?

926
01:02:17,800 --> 01:02:18,930
It's the VIP theater, isn't it?

927
01:02:19,000 --> 01:02:20,400
You can't!

928
01:02:22,070 --> 01:02:23,610
You can't be seen together.

929
01:02:23,670 --> 01:02:25,210
Is he with someone?

930
01:02:25,270 --> 01:02:27,010
No!

931
01:02:28,940 --> 01:02:30,480
Wait a moment please.

932
01:02:37,820 --> 01:02:40,890
It's the same woman from last time who's with him right now, isn't it?

933
01:02:41,220 --> 01:02:42,360
I don't know.

934
01:02:42,420 --> 01:02:44,160
Don't pretend that you don't.

935
01:02:44,960 --> 01:02:46,830
Who exactly is this woman?

936
01:02:46,900 --> 01:02:48,160
I don't know.

937
01:02:48,900 --> 01:02:50,100
Who is it?

938
01:02:50,170 --> 01:02:51,370
I don't know.

939
01:02:53,240 --> 01:02:53,970
- Who is it?
- I don't know.

940
01:02:54,970 --> 01:02:57,310
Should I just go in and confirm it myself?

941
01:03:01,240 --> 01:03:02,780
You won't let anyone know?

942
01:03:02,840 --> 01:03:07,380
Tell me, who is it exactly?

943
01:03:07,580 --> 01:03:08,720
I don't know.

944
01:03:09,520 --> 01:03:10,520
He's with a woman, isn't he?

945
01:03:10,850 --> 01:03:11,920
There's a woman, isn't there?

946
01:03:11,920 --> 01:03:12,920
What?

947
01:03:13,720 --> 01:03:15,460
No? There's no woman?

948
01:03:16,390 --> 01:03:19,730
Who is it? Who?!

949
01:03:25,600 --> 01:03:26,740
You intend to have supper here?

950
01:03:26,800 --> 01:03:27,870
Aren't you treating?

951
01:03:27,940 --> 01:03:28,740
Yes, my treat.

952
01:03:28,800 --> 01:03:30,870
You haven't treated for a long time!

953
01:03:41,020 --> 01:03:42,750
Your food is here!

954
01:03:43,620 --> 01:03:45,150
This looks delicious.

955
01:03:54,360 --> 01:03:55,360
Thank you!

956
01:03:56,500 --> 01:03:57,770
How do you do?

957
01:04:01,900 --> 01:04:03,570
I'm in a bit of a fix right now...

958
01:04:04,040 --> 01:04:07,310
Just pretend you didn't see me. Sorry.

959
01:04:27,660 --> 01:04:30,200
Gu Ae Jeong, what's up with you now?

960
01:05:00,960 --> 01:05:02,230
Where are you?

961
01:05:02,760 --> 01:05:04,300
Please watch the movie alone.

962
01:05:04,430 --> 01:05:06,370
I won't go inside.

963
01:05:07,500 --> 01:05:11,370
To me, this is already my limit.

964
01:05:11,840 --> 01:05:13,910
Now it's time for me to muster my energy and return to reality.

965
01:05:13,980 --> 01:05:17,510
I've already bought everything you wanted: Coke, popcorn, and potatoes.

966
01:05:19,510 --> 01:05:21,520
What's wrong with you?

967
01:05:21,580 --> 01:05:24,050
I'm really scared of that potato.

968
01:05:24,120 --> 01:05:28,060
Are you avoiding me because you're scared that I'll catch that chicken?

969
01:05:28,120 --> 01:05:30,060
Yes, I'm scared...

970
01:05:31,190 --> 01:05:33,600
I'm scared of the fact that I actually don't mind being bullied by you,

971
01:05:33,660 --> 01:05:35,260
and even think of letting you continue to bully me.

972
01:05:35,330 --> 01:05:37,130
I am scared of that aspect of myself.

973
01:05:37,330 --> 01:05:41,600
=I would really like to be more easy-going and open.=

974
01:05:41,670 --> 01:05:45,270
I've trained so hard over these past ten years to reach my current state. It was difficult to become so easy-going.

975
01:05:45,340 --> 01:05:49,880
I'm very afraid that if I let my heart waver now, my past effort will be wasted.

976
01:05:50,410 --> 01:05:54,680
Dok Go Jin, you might currently be fearless because of your fixation with me...

977
01:05:54,750 --> 01:05:58,150
But aren't you afraid that I'd decide to really hold on to you and not let you go?
